entries.femaleVariant: That is not all of them.
I believe... Yes, that is the last of Yorinobu's people.
I believe a war has just begun.
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="見事だ" t="Excellent." b="" a=""/>
I await you.
It's just weird, that's all. You call the biggest board meeting in a decade without invitin' your own sister?
I repeat. Internal security has not been compromised. Over.
All systems are go for me. Standing by. Over.
Yes, sir. Everything is under control. Over.
Mh-hm-hm! This view's to die for! And the air, man, the air...!
Glad they called us here instead of the tower...
Hellman! We are done! We need the AV, now!
These people... they simply left me no choice.
Keep it together.
Did what we had to do.
We have a job to do.
Did what we had to.
This is why I have remained outside, uninvolved.
So as not to have to make decisions such as these.
Need to keep it together, for all our sakes!
I need do nothing.
It is just that…
Well, it's not like she has any official position…
Psh. Since when do you have to be official to pull the strings?
Those gold fingers of hers? They're a symbol – wraps peole around them. Just like she did her dad.
There's your answer, then. Our new Emperor Arasaka isn't about to get tangled up in any gold fingers.
You're right, though, it is a little weird...
Mhm. Goddamn Smasher... Can you believe it? 'Saka 'lites like us steppin' aside for some punk-ass ex-merc? So what if he's biopodded?
Maybe it's just temporary.
Yorinobu must've had a good reason to drag him out of his cave. Looks like he's not gonna crawl back in there anytime soon.
I will go left. The right side is yours.
There is a netrunner in the building. I will eliminate him.
It is clear inside. I will monitor the situation from here.
I will reach you shortly, V.
They know you are here.
You must neutralize them. All of them.
I am in the bedroom in the central part of the building.
Anders, you get the AV.
But first, we must... neutralize the four guards. V? Is your task clear?
But first, we must... neutralize the four guards. Takemura, V? Is your task clear?
We will take the left side, through the garden.
I will obstruct their communications so that no support arrives.
Careful, now. There are five more guards outside. And a dweller in the garage on the left.
One guard in the courtyard, another near the pool. Number three – on the terrace, the last inside.
I'm nearing the residence.
What have you done?! Now you will have to face them all!
Patrol, two men.
You take one, I will handle the other myself.
Neutralized. Down to the last.
Good. I am disabling lockdown. I await you.
Good. Land by the pool.
Please.
[Get in]
War's… a bit much, innit? Though a loaded word for any Arasaka.
entries.maleVariant: War's a bit much, isn't it? Though a loaded word for any Arasaka.

entries.femaleVariant: You will not need this anymore…
He did not have time to call for backup... Good.
That gives us the upper hand, but we must hurry.
Uh-huh. We "neutralize."
Roger that. Over and out.
Anders, you get the AV.
No blood was spilled – this is good.
Just counting bodies. You, me and Hellman makes three. Actually, two and a half.
Just counting bodies. You, me, Goro and Hellman makes four. Actually, three and a half.
Is that what you believe?
There is Oda, too. We will meet him there.
Oda would be here, if you had not…
He was provided with excellent care.
It was him or me, Hanako.
Pretty quick to get back on his feet.
My brother is not all of Arasaka. Not yet, at least.
He knows this well. It is the reason he surrounds himself with criminals like Adam Smasher.
That supposed to make me feel better?
My father was "on his own." And he built an empire.
Reality is we're on our own.
Anyway, against all Arasaka and its armies? That's not much.
For now. Things could still get ugly.
Rather not get your hands dirty?
Yet now…
For now. Could get a lot uglier down the line.
You ready for that?
Always.
Rather not dirty your hands, huh?
Chances are you'll have to soon enough.
I am well aware.
<mothertongue l="jpn" m="Kuso." b="" a=" We must beware of the mech."/>
[Get out] "Neutralize." Got it.
We are waiting.
Can we not simply depart… and leave her?
entries.maleVariant: Can we not simply depart… and leave him?

entries.femaleVariant: V! Get in!
V! Arasaka-sama –  run and get her! We will be there soon!
